d processing, experiment management, and feature engineering\"]\n  \n    %% Bottom: External Systems\n    videos[\"Subsea Videos<br/>Raw video data\"]\n    images[\"Subsea Images<br/>Raw image data\"]\n    reports[\"Subsea Reports<br/>Structured/unstructured reports\"]\n    storage[\"Object Storage<br/>AWS S3, Azure Blob, GCP, On-Prem\"]\n    processing[\"Distributed Processing Engines<br/>Spark, Dask, Batch Jobs\"]\n    featurestore[\"Feature Store<br/>Engineered features\"]\n    experiment[\"Experiment Management<br/>Tracking & registry\"]\n    governance[\"Governance Service<br/>Security, compliance, audit\"]\n  \n    %% Connections\n    subsea_user --> subsea_package\n    videos --> subsea_package\n    images --> subsea_package\n    reports --> subsea_package\n    subsea_package --> storage\n    subsea_package --> processing\n    subsea_package --> featurestore\n    subsea_package --> experiment\n    subsea_package --> governance\n```\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n```{mermaid}\nflowchart TD\n    subgraph Users\n        A[Subsea CV Team]\n    end\n  subgraph Ingestion\n        B1[Raw Videos/Images/Reports]\n        B2[Ingestion API]\n    end\n  subgraph Storage\n        C1[AWS S3]\n        C2[Azure Blob]\n        C3[GCP Storage]\n        C4[Petrobras On-Prem Storage]\n    end\n  subgraph Processing\n        D1[Distributed Processing Engine]\n        D2[Databricks/Spark]\n        D3[Dask]\n        D4[Batch/Streaming Jobs]\n    end\n  subgraph FeatureStore\n        E1[Feature Engineering Module]\n        E2[Feature Store]\n    end\n  subgraph Experiment\n        F1[Experiment Tracking]\n        F2[Model Registry]\n    end\n  subgraph Governance\n        G1[Security & Compliance]\n        G2[Audit Logging]\n    end\n  A --> B2\n    B1 --> B2\n    B2 --> C1\n    B2 --> C2\n    B2 --> C3\n    B2 --> C4\n  C1 --> D1\n    C2 --> D1\n    C3 --> D1\n    C4 --> D1\n  D1 --> D2\n    D1 --> D3\n    D1 --> D4\n  D2 --> E1\n    D3 --> E1\n    D4 --> E1\n  E1 --> E2\n    E2 --> F1\n    F1 -->